## 🎯 What is AtoM?

**AtoM (Access to Memory)** is an open-source, web-based archival description application developed by Artefactual Systems. It's trusted by national archives, universities, and cultural institutions worldwide for managing archival collections according to international standards (ISAD(G), ISAAR(CPF), ISDF, ISDIAH).

**AtoM handles core archival workflow beautifully.**

---

## 🚀 What AtoM Extensions Adds

AtoM Extensions transforms AtoM into a **complete GLAM solution** (Galleries, Libraries, Archives, Museums) with modern architecture, international compliance, and enterprise features.

---

